						               													<description>Take to the High seas as commander of one of three formidable fleets and cut a swathe through the storied Oceans of Thargos! You'll face an endless array of dangers, from the seas themselves, the killers that sail them and the dark horrors which lurk beneath them. Will you prevail or will a watery grave be your only prize?&amp;#10;&amp;#226;&amp;#128;&amp;#139;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Command a war galley in a gritty fantasy setting using solo/coop or vs game modes. You decide what risks to take to avoid being sunk. You complete epic voyages for the ultimate prize.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players choose their fleet, which vessels to play on specific voyages and then manage the hull integrity, crew morale and supplies as you come up against pirates, enemy fleets, foul weather and sea creatures througgh the use of an event card deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You then roll dice to determine the success of each encounter, choosing to pursue a sea battle or make a hasty retreat to fight another day for example. Ecah vessel has unique attributes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game is won on a Victory Point basis with rewards for completing voyages, sinking enemy tonnage and more. The game ends after completring all 5 voyages included.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;WGoT also contains bonus Mission Cards for the Heroes of Thargos CG enabling the two games to be combined.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
